OL,3,CEmbattled fire boss quits in social
OL,4,Cmedia post alleging threats and
OL,5,Cdishonesty
OL,7,FMr Lee described it as "another post
OL,8,Foffice" referring to the scandal over
OL,9,Fthe mistreatment of Postmasters.
OL,11,F"I will not be gagged"
OL,13,FHe wrote "I have been threatened
OL,14,Frepeatedly, mainly to stay quiet on
OL,15,Fvital subjects in the public interest.
OL,17,F"I will not be gagged. Nor will I
OL,18,Fdestroy my family with vast legal
OL,19,Fbills. I have therefore resigned in
OL,20,Forder to do what is right."
