OL,5,Cdishonesty
OL,7,FHis resignation follows a tumultuous
OL,8,Fperiod for the fire service. Lee was
OL,9,Fsuspended earlier in the week pending
OL,10,Fan investigation into governance
OL,11,Fconcerns, the details of which haven't
OL,12,Fbeen published.
OL,14,FIn his post, Lee accused some parts of
OL,15,Fthe organisation of dishonesty,
OL,16,Fcontributing to what he described as a
OL,17,Ftoxic environment within the service.
