OL,7,FThe suspension was to be ratified by
OL,8,Fthe full Fire Authority on 14th
OL,9,FOctober, with an independent
OL,10,Finvestigation into Lee's conduct
OL,11,Fexpected to follow.
OL,13,FIn a statement earlier this week, West
OL,14,FMidlands Fire and Rescue Authority
OL,15,Fexpressed regret over the decision to
OL,16,Fsuspend Lee, calling it "hugely
OL,17,Fdeflating" and acknowledging the
OL,18,Fpublic concern it would raise.
