OL,7,FThe authority emphasised that the
OL,8,Fsuspension followed independent
OL,9,Fadvice, and promised that an external
OL,10,Finvestigation into governance concerns
OL,11,Fraised by Lee would continue.
OL,13,FDespite these assurances, Lee's
OL,14,Fresignation and public allegations
OL,15,Fhave cast a shadow over the leadership
OL,16,Fof WMFS, with his accusations of
OL,17,Fdishonesty and threats likely to fuel
OL,18,Ffurther scrutiny of how the service is
OL,19,Fgoverned.
