OL,7,FLee's public statements, however,
OL,8,Fsuggest that deeper, unresolved
OL,9,Fconflicts remain within the Fire
OL,10,FAuthority, which could complicate
OL,11,Fefforts to stabilise the service.
OL,13,FThe Fire Authority is set to meet next
OL,14,FMonday, where the legal report on Lee,
OL,15,Fhis resignation, and the ongoing
OL,16,Fgovernance issues are expected to
OL,17,Fdominate the agenda.
