OL,7,FIt remains to be seen how the service
OL,8,Fwill address these internal challenges
OL,9,Fwhile continuing to deliver emergency
OL,10,Fservices to the communities of the
OL,11,FWest Midlands.
OL,13,FLee's explosive resignation has
OL,14,Fundoubtedly intensified public
OL,15,Fattention on WMFS, raising critical
OL,16,Fquestions about leadership
OL,17,Ftransparency and the future direction
OL,18,Fof the organisation.
OL,20,FA West Midlands Fire Service
OL,21,Fspokesperson said:
